d></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">Venue</th><td class=\"infobox-data\">Tachi Palace Hotel &amp; Casino</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"infobox-label\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; width=33%\">City</th><td class=\"infobox-data\"><a href=\"/wiki/Lemoore,_California\" title=\"Lemoore, California\">Lemoore, California</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-header\" style=\"background:lightgrey;color:inherit; text-decoration:none;\">Event chronology</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-full-data\"><span></span>\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4em; vertical-align: top\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0\"><a href=\"/wiki/WEC_14\" title=\"WEC 14\">WEC 14: Vengeance</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0.1em 0.2em 0.1em; font-weight: bold;\">WEC 15: Judgment Day\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33%; text-align: center; padding: 0.2em 0 0.2em 0.1em\"><a href=\"/wiki/WEC_16\" title=\"WEC 16\">WEC 16: Clash of the Titans 2</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>WEC 15: Judgment Day</b> was a <a href=\"/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts\" title=\"Mixed martial arts\">mixed martial arts</a> event promoted by <a href=\"/wiki/World_Extreme_Cagefighting\" title=\"World Extreme Cagefighting\">World Extreme Cagefighting</a> on May 19, 2005, at the Tachi Palace Hotel &amp; Casino in <a href=\"/wiki/Lemoore,_California\" title=\"Lemoore, California\">Lemoore, California</a>. The card featured the likes of <a href=\"/wiki/Joe_Riggs\" title=\"Joe Riggs\">Joe Riggs</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Chris_Lytle\" title=\"Chris Lytle\">Chris Lytle</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/James_Irvin_(fighter)\" title=\"James Irvin (fighter)\">James Irvin</a> compete.<sup id=\"cite&#95;ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\"